---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 100
By: Sri Ramakrishna
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Phantom Flux of Life
  - Discernment-Truth=Reality=The Nature of Reality
---
You cannot have real love of God unless you know that the world is
impermanent, only of two days' existence, while its Creator alone is real and
eternal.
